<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA612_04_IH_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema612_04.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema612_04_ih_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="4_green" class="is_star" lang="y">은호와 시은이가 만들려고 하는 입체도형의 이름을 고르세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
          <div class="img_area">
            <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA612_04_IH/0004_01.png" alt="" />
            <p class="text1" lang="y">두 면이 평행하고 합동인 다각형으로 이루어진 입체도형을 만들어 보자.</p>
            <p class="text2" lang="y">
              옆면이 모두 직사각형이고,<br />
              꼭짓점이 8개인<br />
              입체도형을 만들자.
            </p>
            <p class="name1" lang="y">은호</p>
            <p class="name2" lang="y">시은</p>
          </div>
          <div class="dropdown_wrap">
            <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="사각기둥">
              <option></option>
              <option value="삼각기둥"></option>
              <option value="사각기둥"></option>
              <option value="오각기둥"></option>
              <option value="육각기둥"></option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">두 밑면이 평행하고 합동이며, 옆면이 모두 직사각형인 입체도형은 각기둥입니다. 꼭짓점이 8개인 각기둥은 사각기둥입니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
